# Frontend Mentor - QR code component solution

# Frontend Mentor - QR code component

This is a solution to the [git ](https://www.frontendmentor.io/challenges/qr-code-component-iux_sIO_H). Frontend Mentor challenges help you improve your coding skills by building realistic projects

## Overview
This is a Frontend Mento - Qr Code Compentent challenge were I tried to replicate the design of the QR code as much as possible.
This project is built with HTML and CSS only. 
Thanks for checking out this front-end coding challenge.



